response.original_title: Deliveroo: How Do They Really Do It?
response.overview: The secrets of the online food company's success, travelling with the delivery riders, revealing the meals to avoid and which foods stay hot and which do not. Experts and ex-employees reveal the hidden workings of Deliveroo to help show how online delivery really works, and there is a look at branding and marketing innovations - some of which have got Deliveroo into hot water.
response.title: Deliveroo: How Do They Really Do It?
